### Get all teams
GET http://localhost:8080/teams

### Get team by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/teams/1

### Get team by position
GET http://localhost:8080/teams/position/1

### Create new team
POST http://localhost:8080/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": 1,
  "gameId": 1
}

### Create another team
POST http://localhost:8080/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": 2,
  "gameId": 1
}

### Update team
PUT http://localhost:8080/teams/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": 3,
  "gameId": 1
}

### Delete team by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/teams/1

### Delete all teams
DELETE http://localhost:8080/teams